28
00:02:36,020 --> 00:02:38,110
Coach, please don't say that.

29
00:02:38,110 --> 00:02:42,470
Think about it. If he can't even protect his legs, how can he play soccer?

30
00:02:43,450 --> 00:02:46,990
To be honest, his injury is so serious

31
00:02:46,990 --> 00:02:50,410
because he was too desperate to prove himself in this competition.

32
00:02:50,410 --> 00:02:54,520
And our school's team doesn't have proper professional training programs,

33
