after this selection match.

38
00:03:07,390 --> 00:03:12,790
So if he only plays on our school team, it's really a waste of his talent.

39
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:18,140
I just hope you'll reconsider letting him go pro.

40
00:03:56,740 --> 00:03:58,270
Eight...

41
00:04:08,300 --> 00:04:09,600
Why are you here?

42
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:12,120
You're awake? I came to check on you.

43
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:14,560
How are you feeling? Does it hurt?

44
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:20,890
- Chen Huan Er... 
 - I'll call the doctor.

45
00:04:20,890 --> 00:04:23,150
No, no, no! No need.

46
00:04:23,150 --> 00:04:24,740
Painkillers...

47
00:04:25,570 --> 00:04:27,470
This one, right? How many?

48
00:04:27,470 --> 00:04:28,910
One.

49
00:04:28,910 --> 00:04:30,230
Can you be more careful?

50
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:32,720
Sorry, sorry! Really sorry, bro.

51
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,260
Here.

52
00:04:39,010 --> 00:04:40,500
Does it hurt that bad?

53
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:42,400
Of course!

54
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:48,940
The doctor said you need to rest and not move around.

55
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,320
What's that?

56
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:52,840
It's not bone broth, is it?

57
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:54,380
Aunt Hao just brought some over at noon.

58
00:04:54,380 --> 00:04:55,960
I've been drinking it like water these days.

59
00:04:55,960 --> 00:05:00,280
- Then I'll just leave it here. 
 - No, no. I'll drink it.

60
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:02,900
I'd rather finish it quickly and get better sooner.

61
00:05:04,420 --> 00:05:05,470
You know what?

62
00:05:05,470 --> 00:05:08,150
Last night, I dreamed I was playing soccer.

63
00:05:08,150 --> 00:05:10,860
I played so well.

64
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:12,710
