65
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:18,100
Thanks.

66
00:05:23,230 --> 00:05:25,790
Why were you so careless?

67
00:05:28,180 --> 00:05:30,470
Maybe because

68
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:33,420
I wanted to win too badly this time.

69
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:45,740
I've had enough. This medicine makes me drowsy.

70
00:05:45,740 --> 00:05:47,600
Then go ahead and sleep.

71
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,890
I'll leave when Aunt Lin gets here.

72
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:13,820
 This was the first time I had ever seen Xi Chi so down and defeated. 

73
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:17,790
 He's always been bright, optimistic, and full of energy. 

74
00:06:17,790 --> 00:06:20,890
 Always the one encouraging and uplifting us. 

75
00:06:20,890 --> 00:06:24,380
 But at that moment, I realized that he had been 

76
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:30,300
 silently digesting all his negative emotions on his own. 

77
00:06:39,550 --> 00:06:41,200
Who is it?

78
00:06:42,180 --> 00:06:44,630
- Li Na, how come you're here? 
 - Yi Fan, I came to see you!

79
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:47,390
You came as well, Huan Er.

80
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:49,180
Sorry... can I use the restroom?

81
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:50,960
- Over here, this way. Go ahead. 
 - Go on.

82
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:54,000
We especially went to that old shop where you used to love buying pastries

83
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,020
and got some for you.

84
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:56,880
Try them and see if they still taste the same.

85
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:57,740
Thank you.

86
00:06:57,740 --> 00:06:59,520
If I hadn't come, you wouldn't have come either.

87
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:01,540
- You followed the scent, right? 
 - That's right.

88
00:07:01,540 --> 00:07:03,860
If you're here, how could I not be?

89
00:07:03,860 --> 00:07:05,270
Have some tea.

90
00:07:05,270 --> 00:07:06,740
Thanks.

91
00:07:06,740 --> 00:07:10,630
You two have been working and still made time to visit me.

92
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:12,630
It must be exhausting. I really appreciate it.

93
00:07:12,630 --> 00:07:14,560
What are you saying? Why are you thanking us?

94
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,740
Are you going to act all formal with us?

95
00:07:16,740 --> 00:07:17,860
Song Hang said

96
00:07:17,860 --> 00:07:20,910
