97
00:07:20,910 --> 00:07:24,740
As long as he does proper rehab, he'll fully recover with no problem.

98
00:07:24,740 --> 00:07:26,180
Exactly.

99
00:07:26,180 --> 00:07:30,230
But Yi Fan, why do you look so worn out lately?

100
00:07:31,030 --> 00:07:33,830
Why are you tearing up as we talk?

101
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:37,480
Yeah. Is it because it's exhausting running back and forth between the clinic and the ward?

102
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,660
You need to rest.

103
00:07:38,660 --> 00:07:41,440
Just tell us if there's anything wrong. No need to be polite with us.

104
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,960
I'm fine, really.

105
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:44,760
I know my own limits.

106
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:47,270
But these past few days, I have been a little worried.

107
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:48,630
I need you guys' advice.

108
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:53,240
Do you think I should let him take a year off from school?

109
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,520
Give him some time to adjust?

110
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:59,130
- That could work. 
 - Aunt Lin, Jing Xi Chi can do it.

111
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:00,630
Don't worry.

112
00:08:00,630 --> 00:08:04,540
If needed, I, along with Song Cong, can tutor him.

113
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:05,860
He'll catch up for sure.

114
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:09,940
Yes, I'll tell Song Cong that once school is out, he should come over to tutor him.

115
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:13,490
- No problem. 
 - Yes, that should work.

116
00:08:13,490 --> 00:08:14,710
Thank you, Huan Er.

117
00:08:14,710 --> 00:08:15,910
It's nothing, really.

118
00:08:15,910 --> 00:08:17,590
I'm really jealous of you two.

119
00:08:17,590 --> 00:08:21,510
