120
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,860
Oh, come on.

121
00:08:22,860 --> 00:08:25,390
Here, try this pastry. See if it still tastes the same.

122
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:27,060
Thanks, I got it.

123
00:08:27,060 --> 00:08:28,880
I'll just have one.

124
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:35,130
Take a guess! Guess what we brought you?

125
00:08:36,010 --> 00:08:37,460
What is it?

126
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:43,960
I was just relieved that being in the hospital meant no homework...

127
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:46,350
- But you guys... 
 - You wish!

128
00:08:46,350 --> 00:08:48,880
Starting today, we're tutoring you every day.

129
00:08:49,630 --> 00:08:52,500
