Here.

211
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:25,630
Why are you here?

212
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:27,450
I came to see you.

213
00:14:30,230 --> 00:14:32,070
Are you tired?

214
00:14:35,870 --> 00:14:37,320
Here.

215
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:40,260
Thanks.

216
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:55,490
Is it going well?

217
00:14:56,180 --> 00:14:57,890
Not too bad.

218
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:05,800
It's just that...

219
00:15:07,131 --> 00:15:10,981
I think I underestimated how hard this would be.

220
00:15:16,230 --> 00:15:18,700
I've actually thought it through.

221
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:24,060
Many great soccer players have been injured before.

222
00:15:24,060 --> 00:15:27,660
This injury of mine is nothing in comparison.

223
00:15:32,350 --> 00:15:34,180
But, Huan Er...

224
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:42,700
I feel like my body... is not listening to me anymore.

225
00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:52,060
Perhaps... God is giving me a warning.

226
00:15:55,940 --> 00:15:58,410
I should have quit earlier

227
00:16:00,300 --> 00:16:03,770
so I wouldn't have caused my parents so much worry.

228
00:16:10,030 --> 00:16:12,510
I've been thinking a lot lately.

229
00:16:14,420 --> 00:16:17,970
You know, they both have their own jobs and careers.

230
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:25,180
I can't just let them keep living in constant worry because of me, right?

231
00:16:28,630 --> 00:16:31,540
This is just the beginning, isn't it?

232
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:34,420
You have to be patient with your body.

233
00:16:34,420 --> 00:16:36,030
Listen to me.

234
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:39,508
You will definitely get better.

235
00:16:39,508 --> 00:16:42,400
Once you're well, we'll go to school together.

236
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:49,270
You have no idea. In the mornings when Song Cong and I walked to school, he actually...

237
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:51,150
He what?

238
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:55,110
He started explaining math problems to me!

239
00:16:58,540 --> 00:17:02,580
You've got to save me. Cong is driving me crazy.

240
00:17:02,580 --> 00:17:04,150
You need to save me.

241
00:17:04,150 --> 00:17:05,730
Chen Huan Er.

242
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:09,740
Don't come to see me anymore.

243
00:17:12,081 --> 00:17:14,746
You don't want us to visit you now?

244
00:17:14,746 --> 00:17:16,196
It's not that.

245
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:20,001
Look, all I do every day is rehabilitation.

246
00:17:20,001 --> 00:17:21,845
There's nothing else going on.

247
00:17:21,845 --> 00:17:23,920
I don't want to delay your studies.

248
00:17:24,940 --> 00:17:27,020
That won't happen.

249
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:32,740
Fine, then I'll tell Cong not to come.

250
00:17:34,020 --> 00:17:36,110
I mean,

251
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:40,000
you shouldn't come either.

252
00:17:46,150 --> 00:17:47,560
I'll help you.

253
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,760
Here.

254
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:50,420
Here.

255
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:52,560
Come on, go slow.

256
00:17:52,560 --> 00:17:55,690
- Here. I've got you. 
 - I'm fine. I can do it.

257
00:17:55,690 --> 00:17:57,490
It's fine. I can manage.

